verbose_text: miR-106b-5p targets CTSA to suppress the invasion and metastasis of colorectal cancer, but miR-106b-5p promotes stem cell like properties of hepatocellular carcinoma cells through targeting PTEN via a PI3K / Akt signaling pathway.
evidence: miR-106b-5p promotes stem cell-like properties of hepatocellular carcinoma cells through targeting PTEN
